1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:04,240
Fixation is a free and open-source framework 
for experimental eye movement research,  

2
00:00:04,240 --> 00:00:08,160
agnostic to the source of the raw gaze stream 
and can be used with any eye tracking platform,  

3
00:00:08,160 --> 00:00:11,040
by mapping data to a JSON format 
and streaming it in real time.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:16,640
A researcher can record and visualize gaze data 
and export it for analysis using an offline  

5
00:00:16,640 --> 00:00:20,080
web application, without proprietary 
components or licensing restrictions.

6
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:24,160
We leverage web technologies to 
address data privacy concerns,  

7
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:29,760
and demonstrate support for high-frequency 
recording and real-time visualization.

